00:20:43,140 --> 00:20:48,200
Compass aims to give people
the habits, tools, knowledge,

421
00:20:48,200 --> 00:20:50,620
and capacity to act
from their own most

422
00:20:50,620 --> 00:20:52,900
fundamental commitments.

