00:21:12,660 --> 00:21:16,620
and whole human
beings that will be

430
00:21:16,620 --> 00:21:20,220
functioning in the digital age.

431
00:21:20,220 --> 00:21:23,580
At Compass, our mission is to
help students see themselves

